{"tid":2145648,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"金管局向財金機構發信　稱外國政府制裁在港「無法律效力」","createTime":"2020-08-08T07:01:02.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-08T07:50:52.000Z","uid":105567,"like":4,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"3c23ecca970f535115f164f4883174f948a61d91","tid":2145648,"uid":105567,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-08T07:01:02.000Z","msg":"咁請問點解香港d銀行要跟FATCA？<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hangseng.com/zh-hk/fatca/faq/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hangseng.com%2Fzh-hk%2Ffatca%2Ffaq%2F&d=973ie4zpYy9ax4bL%2F%2BCgDIjkqoP0ISDA%2F8fQ3RVu%2FF4%3D&h=aea7816b\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.hangseng.com/zh-hk/fatca/faq/</a><br />\n<br />\nFATCA全稱為《外國賬戶稅務合規法案》，是美國為防止美國納稅人逃避美國稅項而制定的一項新法律。<br />\n<br />\n該項法案由美國財政部（財政部）和美國國稅局（國稅局）制定，旨在防止美國人士（請參閱詞彙表）利用銀行及其他金融機構逃避其收入及資產應繳的美國稅款，鼓勵他們更嚴格地遵守稅法。<br />\n<br />\n==========================================<br />\n<br />\n預期全球大部分國家／地區將與美國政府就遵守FATCA簽訂政府間協議(IGA)。這些協議將使FATCA法例變成這些國家／地區本地法律的一部分。（有關政府間協議的定義請參閱詞彙表）<br />\n<br />\n《港區國安法》在 6 月底實施後，美國啟動制裁香港的行動，財政部在當地時間昨日（7 日）宣布制裁名單，包括 11 名中港官員，包括夏寶龍、張曉明、鄭雁雄、駱惠寧、林鄭月娥、鄭若驊、李家超、曾國衞、鄧炳強、陳國基，以及盧偉聰。金管局今日（8 日）向所有認可機構的行政總裁發信，表示外國政府的單方面制裁舉動在香港「沒有法律效力」，各間機構要有所區分，小心評估風險，「並須致力公平對待客戶。」<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.thestandnews.com/politics/%E5%88%B6%E8%A3%81-11-%E5%AE%98-%E9%87%91%E7%AE%A1%E5%B1%80%E5%90%91%E8%B2%A1%E9%87%91%E6%A9%9F%E6%A7%8B%E7%99%BC%E4%BF%A1-%E7%A8%B1%E5%A4%96%E5%9C%8B%E6%94%BF%E5%BA%9C%E5%88%B6%E8%A3%81%E5%9C%A8%E6%B8%AF-%E7%84%A1%E6%B3%95%E5%BE%8B%E6%95%88%E5%8A%9B/?fbclid=IwAR0f19MpYtlOzxWWvMckKT0QyKcYyKPO2EEsjbJt6Tj51kNQaUyTBdK109k\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%25E5%2588%25B6%25E8%25A3%2581-11-%25E5%25AE%2598-%25E9%2587%2591%25E7%25AE%25A1%25E5%25B1%2580%25E5%2590%2591%25E8%25B2%25A1%25E9%2587%2591%25E6%25A9%259F%25E6%25A7%258B%25E7%2599%25BC%25E4%25BF%25A1-%25E7%25A8%25B1%25E5%25A4%2596%25E5%259C%258B%25E6%2594%25BF%25E5%25BA%259C%25E5%2588%25B6%25E8%25A3%2581%25E5%259C%25A8%25E6%25B8%25AF-%25E7%2584%25A1%25E6%25B3%2595%25E5%25BE%258B%25E6%2595%2588%25E5%258A%259B%2F%3Ffbclid%3DIwAR0f19MpYtlOzxWWvMckKT0QyKcYyKPO2EEsjbJt6Tj51kNQaUyTBdK109k&d=973ie4zpYy9ax4bL%2F%2BCgDIjkqoP0ISDA%2F8fQ3RVu%2FF4%3D&h=72c582c5\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%25E5%2588%25B6%25E8%25A3%2581-11-%25E5%25AE%2598-%25E9%2587%2591%25E7%25AE%25A1%25E5%25B1%2580%25E5%2590%2591%25E8%25B2%25A1%25E9%2587%2591%25E6%25A9%259F%25E6%25A7%258B%25E7%2599%25BC%25E4%25BF%25A1-%25E7%25A8%25B1%25E5%25A4%2596%25E5%259C%258B%25E6%2594%25BF%25E5%25BA%259C%25E5%2588%25B6%25E8%25A3%2581%25E5%259C%25A8%25E6%25B8%25AF-%25E7%2584%25A1%25E6%25B3%2595%25E5%25BE%258B%25E6%2595%2588%25E5%258A%259B%2F%3Ffbclid%3DIwAR0f19MpYtlOzxWWvMckKT0QyKcYyKPO2EEsjbJt6Tj51kNQaUyTBdK109k&h=29939743\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.thestandnews.com/politics/%E5%88%B6%E8%A3%81-11-%E5%AE%98-%E9%87%91%E7%AE%A1%E5%B1%80%E5%90%91%E8%B2%A1%E9%87%91%E6%A9%9F%E6%A7%8B%E7%99%BC%E4%BF%A1-%E7%A8%B1%E5%A4%96%E5%9C%8B%E6%94%BF%E5%BA%9C%E5%88%B6%E8%A3%81%E5%9C%A8%E6%B8%AF-%E7%84%A1%E6%B3%95%E5%BE%8B%E6%95%88%E5%8A%9B/?fbclid=IwAR0f19MpYtlOzxWWvMckKT0QyKcYyKPO2EEsjbJt6Tj51kNQaUyTBdK109k</a>"},{"pid":"9a0b04fbedcc3f5adfefb57a743a3970bf07a123","tid":2145648,"uid":2267,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-08T07:04:19.000Z","msg":"美國：邊個唔跟，就邊個無得用美金結算"},{"pid":"25c826664955467a434624bc53ffe1fb537c79d9","tid":2145648,"uid":2054,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-08T07:14:27.000Z","msg":"你咪睇下銀行聽邊個<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/silly.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"90eb078567d60bd2b8d554c5bc691842984953ec","tid":2145648,"uid":340796,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-08T07:24:48.000Z","msg":"如果SEC register<br />\n或者跟FATCA 嗰啲已經中咗sanction scope<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n咩叫在港?<br />\n間公司實體在港, 但筆資產offshore, 叫唔叫在港?<img src